	<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.222222328186035px; line-height: 17.77777862548828px; ">This stunning looking black carved oil burner is made from natural soap stone, which is also a natural heat resistant. With all of it delicate carvings and intricate markings it makes a beautiful piece to add to any room or even to be given as a gift. The delicate carvings let out the glow from the candle whilst also spreading an even aroma around the room. This oil burner is approx. 8cms tall. To use simply add a few drops of the fragrance oil to a small amount of water, place a tea light underneath and let it get to work.</span></p>
